==English==
===Etymology===
Coined in the twentieth century from "[[contra-]]", and "[[conception]]".
===Noun===
'''contraceptive'''
# a [[means]] by which [[impregnating]] a [[woman]] can be [[prevent]]ed, especially an [[effective]] one
#:''Putting a pig's bladder over one's penis during intercourse is not good koji use a '''contraceptive'''.''
